These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, may, july
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, lavender, brown
1. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Birthday   | july  | october    | may      |
| Color     | lavender     | grey      | brown |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, ivory, black
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, project-manager, photographer
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the project-manager##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person who likes black##1
4. the person eating kale is the person who likes ivory##1
5. the lawyer is between the fan of gospel and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Color   | black  | ivory | amber |
| Job           | photographer | lawyer     | project-manager       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, august, april
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, car, trike
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person driving the trike and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday          | december  | april     | august     |
| Transport           | trike | van  | car   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, january
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, video-games, singing
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is between the paramedic and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday    | august       | january  | october   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Hobby   | singing | traveling     | video-games      |

