.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different games are played: poker, bridge, billiard
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, cricket, swimming
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is between the fan of gospel and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Game          | billiard    | poker     | bridge      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| Sport           | cricket     | cycling       | swimming     |

