.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pumpkin
House: art-deco, townhouse, palace
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, argentine, german
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is the art-deco house##1
3. the argentine is between the person eating pineapple and the owner of the horse##2
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | pumpkin    |
| House         | townhouse | palace      | art-deco |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | argentine     | german        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

