.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, pony
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the egyptian is between the person eating radish and the person driving the car##2
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the egyptian is between the nigerian and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Nationality         | mexican | egyptian | nigerian |
| Pet   | lizard      | pony | ferret   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

