.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, skiing
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, light-blue-climbing
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, green, light-blue
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the architect is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's sport is skiing##2
5. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Sport      | volleyball       | parkour      | skiing      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | light-blue-climbing | chess      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Color   | green     | light-blue          | amber       |

