.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, musician, librarian
There 3 different types of food: carrot, orange, garlic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, italian
1. the librarian is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the musician is on the left of the italian##1
3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the person eating orange and the person eating carrot##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Job      | librarian     | musician | security-guard      |
| Food         | orange  | garlic       | carrot |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    | italian     |

