.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, bellflower
3 different games are played: go, snooker, canasta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, spanish
1. the person who growslily is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who growslily is between the person playing snooker and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Flower      | daisy | lily      | bellflower            |
| Game           | go | canasta | snooker |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | australian    | spanish        |

