2. the pilot is on the right of the pakistani##1
3. the nurse is between the person drinking coffee and the american##2
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | architect | nurse        | pilot       |
| Beverage   | juice | mirinda | coffee |
| Nationality           | american     | pakistani         | australian  |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | tennis       | basketball  |

