1. the person playing scrabble is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Game      | domino    | scrabble          | snooker |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| Flower   | aconite    | orchid    | daffodil      |

