.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, singing
3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, rat
City: san-francisco, rome, prague
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, march, july
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the person who's birthday is in october and the owner of the horse##2
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to rome is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby       | singing | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Pet         | horse   | rat       | mouse        |
| City       | prague | san-francisco   | rome         |
| Birthday   | july    | march     | october         |

