2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who growsazalea is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | cricket  | snowboarding     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| Pet           | dog        | pony   | hamster  |
| Flower     | aconite      | tulip   | azalea |

