1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
6. the writer is between the engineer and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Job           | lawyer   | writer   | engineer |
| Sport   | biathlon | ice-hockey   | rowing     |
| Birthday   | july     | september      | march    |
| Pet           | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse    |

