.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, blue, brown
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, october, june
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the fan of disco is between the person who likes ivory and the person who's birthday is in february##2
4. the fan of reggae is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who likes blue and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Color      | ivory | brown     | blue        |
| Birthday         | october   | june | february |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

