.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
House: gothic-revival, palace, farmhouse
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, juice
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the palace house is the person driving the car##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the car##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the farmhouse house is between the person driving the tram and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
6. the person drinking juice is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| House         | palace     | farmhouse    | gothic-revival        |
| Beverage       | hot-chocolate | juice   | almond-milk   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 